  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wabi-Sabi</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world of bouncing mushrooms—a space embodying the essence of Zen.<br>What are these melancholic yet endearing mushrooms trying to tell us?<br>Their determined struggles will inspire courage in the hearts of all who witness them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls for Relaxing Play</strong><br>Dive in and enjoy intuitive controls—no overthinking required.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Addictive Feel and Satisfying Physics</strong><br>Smooth, squishy, and irresistibly fun mechanics you won’t get enough of.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Variety of Gimmicks and Skins</strong><br>Customize your mushrooms with unique skins and even a charming Japanese <i>shichirin</i> (charcoal grill).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fun Collecting and Exploring</strong><br>Gather coins to unlock skins through a gacha system or embark on a treasure hunt to collect golden axes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=516 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Touch of Eastern Mysticism</strong><br>Immerse yourself in a world where the concepts of \"Wabi-Sabi\" and \"Zen\" come alive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Guidelines for Content Sharing and Streaming</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find the guidelines for video streaming and content sharing on the USAYA website.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wabi-Sabi</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a world of bouncing mushrooms—a space embodying the essence of Zen.<br>What are these melancholic yet endearing mushrooms trying to tell us?<br>Their determined struggles will inspire courage in the hearts of all who witness them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls for Relaxing Play</strong><br>Dive in and enjoy intuitive controls—no overthinking required.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Addictive Feel and Satisfying Physics</strong><br>Smooth, squishy, and irresistibly fun mechanics you won’t get enough of.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></